WEBVTT

00:11.670 --> 00:15.380
[2010]

00:20.320 --> 00:20.870
Zhang.

00:21.390 --> 00:21.990
Good work.

00:22.070 --> 00:23.000
Thank you.

00:23.640 --> 00:24.800
You're calling him Zhang already.

00:24.800 --> 00:25.760
Why act like you've fraternized with him?

00:25.760 --> 00:26.690
Call him Senior.

00:27.670 --> 00:28.760
This girlfriend of yours

00:28.760 --> 00:30.160
is so energetic.

00:30.440 --> 00:31.980
She must've crossed mountains

00:31.980 --> 00:34.520
and ridges to get here
from Jingzhou Police Academy.

00:34.520 --> 00:35.560
What does it mean?

00:35.790 --> 00:37.000
"This girlfriend of yours"?

00:37.000 --> 00:38.640
How many girlfriends do you have?

00:38.640 --> 00:40.220
Were you talking about Lili?

00:40.220 --> 00:42.280
Who's Lili? I demand an explanation!

00:42.280 --> 00:44.210
That was just a random expression.

00:45.880 --> 00:46.880
This is for you.

00:46.900 --> 00:48.330
Eat it somewhere.

00:49.120 --> 00:50.150
Do you think I'm a glutton

00:50.150 --> 00:51.000
like you are?

00:51.880 --> 00:53.640
Did you inform your supervisor
of this visit?

00:53.640 --> 00:54.200
All the cadets

00:54.200 --> 00:55.730
are having a free day today.

00:55.880 --> 00:57.000
I was thinking we could...

00:57.000 --> 00:57.670
Don't even.

00:57.960 --> 01:00.110
I have a lot of things to do
at the station later.

01:00.110 --> 01:01.510
I can't keep you company.

01:03.430 --> 01:04.120
Senior.

01:04.709 --> 01:06.840
Is there much work to do at the station?

01:07.120 --> 01:08.640
That's how police stations are.

01:08.640 --> 01:10.140
Try to be more understanding.

01:10.140 --> 01:11.840
You won't see each other often
when you become

01:11.840 --> 01:14.039
a police officer too and raise a family.

01:14.560 --> 01:16.070
Won't see each other often, huh.

01:16.070 --> 01:17.530
Aren't you a lousy talker?

01:18.910 --> 01:19.590
Alright.

01:19.610 --> 01:20.330
Be good.

01:21.039 --> 01:22.070
We made a pact, didn't we?

01:22.070 --> 01:23.590
As a man, I should focus on my career

01:23.590 --> 01:25.250
and make achievements first.

01:26.310 --> 01:27.150
Fine then.

01:28.710 --> 01:30.640
I'll take it back and eat it myself.

02:06.210 --> 02:07.490
Armbar!

02:09.410 --> 02:10.850
Sorry. I did wrong.

02:10.880 --> 02:12.040
Did you choke?

02:14.080 --> 02:14.810
Do you yield?

02:14.910 --> 02:15.470
Yes, I do.

02:16.000 --> 02:17.460
Stop messing around then.

02:17.470 --> 02:19.240
Lie beside me for a while, will you?

02:19.240 --> 02:21.640
I've been working overtime for three days.

02:27.450 --> 02:28.079
Jin,

02:28.760 --> 02:30.250
you smell so good.

02:31.850 --> 02:32.690
You bet I do.

02:33.110 --> 02:35.040
Your girlfriend has to smell good.

02:47.290 --> 02:50.360
I finally have a home of my own.

04:17.490 --> 04:23.190
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:23.550 --> 04:26.090
[Episode 21]

04:27.270 --> 04:28.070
I'm back!

04:34.510 --> 04:35.870
What were you talking about?

04:35.870 --> 04:36.680
Well...

04:36.960 --> 04:37.960
Just her husband.

04:40.040 --> 04:40.970
What's with him?

04:41.740 --> 04:42.370
Nothing.

04:42.560 --> 04:43.830
He's not available for dinner

04:43.830 --> 04:44.760
with us tonight.

04:45.420 --> 04:46.030
It's okay.

04:46.050 --> 04:47.510
I'll go to dinner with you.

04:48.170 --> 04:49.500
O-Oh, forget it.

04:49.870 --> 04:51.040
Our head just said

04:51.240 --> 04:52.290
you wouldn't be free either.

04:52.290 --> 04:52.930
He asked us

04:52.960 --> 04:54.159
to set out right away.

04:54.900 --> 04:56.230
You're leaving so soon?

04:57.510 --> 04:59.640
Zhou Jin, meet me out here for a second.

05:09.040 --> 05:10.100
I need to talk to you

05:10.480 --> 05:12.080
about a very serious matter.

05:12.510 --> 05:13.360
Jiang Cheng

05:13.950 --> 05:15.040
proposed

05:15.790 --> 05:17.960
to have you as his liaison officer.

05:19.560 --> 05:20.360
I need to ask

05:22.040 --> 05:24.190
for your opinion on this.

05:26.070 --> 05:27.330
Don't force yourself.

05:27.400 --> 05:28.860
If you don't consent to it,

05:28.950 --> 05:29.880
I'll tell him no.

05:40.310 --> 05:41.640
I'm not forcing myself.

05:42.560 --> 05:44.290
I'll take the job and do it well.

06:15.360 --> 06:16.360
What are these?

06:17.070 --> 06:18.190
Some daily necessities

06:18.190 --> 06:19.720
I ordered for you on the way.

06:19.920 --> 06:20.810
If you need anything else,

06:20.810 --> 06:21.760
just let me know.

06:28.920 --> 06:30.270
I feel like it has been a lifetime

06:30.270 --> 06:31.470
since I was last here.

06:40.230 --> 06:40.960
The rent

06:41.350 --> 06:43.210
is paid up till the end of the year.

06:43.360 --> 06:45.159
Just live here without worries.

07:23.430 --> 07:24.600
I am finally home.

07:50.120 --> 07:52.520
There are daily necessities in these bags,

07:53.040 --> 07:55.040
including toothbrushes, tissues,

07:55.270 --> 07:56.240
and some food.

07:56.950 --> 07:57.610
And this...

07:57.920 --> 07:59.720
What food did you buy me?

08:00.070 --> 08:02.330
Any buns with preserved mustard greens?

08:03.410 --> 08:05.120
Let me put these away for you.

08:37.650 --> 08:39.039
You didn't use to be like this.

08:39.039 --> 08:40.610
Since when did you become so particular

08:40.610 --> 08:42.140
about where everything...

09:22.790 --> 09:23.790
Do you need a hand?

09:29.180 --> 09:30.110
Dinner is ready.

09:30.440 --> 09:31.240
Eat it then.

09:33.530 --> 09:34.730
Won't you eat with me?

09:36.360 --> 09:37.620
I'll eat at home later.

09:50.960 --> 09:53.550
I didn't prepare much today
on such short notice.

09:53.550 --> 09:55.120
Whatever else you need later,

09:55.120 --> 09:56.050
just let me know.

09:56.360 --> 09:57.560
I'll order it for you.

10:19.550 --> 10:20.680
I need to go home now.

10:25.050 --> 10:25.650
Jin,

10:26.560 --> 10:28.130
I've never betrayed you.

10:29.280 --> 10:31.040
I haven't been with another woman
in these five years,

10:31.040 --> 10:32.070
not even once.

10:34.480 --> 10:35.440
I know...

10:35.670 --> 10:37.080
I know that former incident

10:37.080 --> 10:38.390
has left you deeply traumatized.

10:38.390 --> 10:39.030
But

10:39.030 --> 10:40.360
I didn't do anything.

10:40.960 --> 10:42.000
I swear to God.

10:45.360 --> 10:46.290
That doesn't...

10:48.030 --> 10:48.960
matter anymore.

10:51.260 --> 10:53.060
Is it because of Jiang Hansheng?

10:54.670 --> 10:56.400
How long have you been with him?

10:56.590 --> 10:57.590
Do you even know him?

10:57.590 --> 10:59.920
What's the fun of being with a guy
like him?

11:10.370 --> 11:11.230
Do you like him?

11:16.150 --> 11:17.210
Then what about me?

11:17.670 --> 11:18.800
Do you still like me?

11:20.870 --> 11:22.630
Don't do this, Jiang Cheng.

11:22.630 --> 11:23.750
Tell me the truth!

11:43.650 --> 11:44.410
Why?

11:50.110 --> 11:50.660
I...

11:55.190 --> 11:56.470
can't persuade myself

11:59.400 --> 12:00.670
to like you again.

12:00.700 --> 12:01.580
But you can!

12:01.960 --> 12:03.150
As long as you want to,

12:03.150 --> 12:04.840
we can go back to how things were!

12:04.840 --> 12:05.960
We can make that happen!

12:05.960 --> 12:07.030
There is no "us" anymore,

12:07.030 --> 12:07.910
Jiang Cheng.

12:09.510 --> 12:10.750
We're over.

12:14.600 --> 12:16.330
There's no way of turning back.

12:17.870 --> 12:18.750
I know

12:19.670 --> 12:21.470
everything you did was for me.

12:23.460 --> 12:25.120
If there's anything you need,

12:26.190 --> 12:27.500
I'll always help.

12:42.020 --> 12:43.680
Do you think I went undercover

12:44.510 --> 12:46.510
just to make you feel guilty about me

12:47.510 --> 12:48.840
so you would compensate

12:49.080 --> 12:49.630
me?

12:52.960 --> 12:53.510
Jin,

12:55.550 --> 12:56.810
I hope you can be happy.

12:59.910 --> 13:00.550
I hope...

13:01.610 --> 13:03.560
you can care for me like you used to.

13:08.870 --> 13:10.150
I'm sorry.

13:12.790 --> 13:14.390
I-I'm really sorry.

13:20.790 --> 13:22.190
So all there is left to say

13:25.030 --> 13:26.790
between us is "sorry" now,

13:27.630 --> 13:28.440
right?

13:46.100 --> 13:47.690
This is my fault.

13:49.390 --> 13:50.790
I did terribly wrong.

13:52.510 --> 13:54.060
My acting was so good...

13:56.530 --> 13:58.980
that you thought I had really dumped you.

14:02.510 --> 14:04.990
It was I who pushed you away.

14:06.480 --> 14:08.340
It was not like that, Jiang Cheng.

14:09.250 --> 14:11.250
You did nothing wrong, Jiang Cheng.

14:12.680 --> 14:14.140
None of this is your fault.

14:16.510 --> 14:17.270
I mean it.

14:17.750 --> 14:19.480
The problem doesn't lie in you,

14:20.720 --> 14:22.030
but in me.

14:24.790 --> 14:25.320
It was...

14:28.440 --> 14:30.000
I who wronged you.

14:31.320 --> 14:32.270
I swear

14:32.740 --> 14:34.220
I'll do whatever I can

14:34.250 --> 14:35.430
to help you get reinstated.

14:35.430 --> 14:36.100
Okay?

14:36.790 --> 14:38.440
It was I who let you down.

14:39.880 --> 14:41.760
I'll do everything you ask me to,

14:42.950 --> 14:43.640
alright?

14:53.930 --> 14:54.930
Jiang Cheng...

15:08.440 --> 15:09.810
Sending a man home this late...

15:09.810 --> 15:10.360
Have you never

15:10.360 --> 15:12.090
thought what he might do to you?

15:12.360 --> 15:13.490
Don't do this again.

16:25.440 --> 16:26.270
Sorry,

16:26.390 --> 16:29.390
the number you dialed
cannot be reached at the moment.

16:32.750 --> 16:33.930
[Zhou Jin]

16:41.740 --> 16:42.500
Jin.

16:42.590 --> 16:43.080
Dad,

16:44.070 --> 16:45.070
where are you?

16:45.100 --> 16:47.030
I'm coming to pick up Hansheng now.

16:47.200 --> 16:47.960
Where are we?

16:48.250 --> 16:49.770
I'm home with Fang.

16:50.750 --> 16:52.080
Hansheng isn't with us.

16:52.280 --> 16:54.010
He said you would be busy today.

16:56.030 --> 16:56.840
Oh, I see.

16:57.920 --> 16:59.100
I was indeed a bit busy today,

16:59.100 --> 17:01.490
occupied by something.
But now the work's all done.

17:01.490 --> 17:03.020
So I want to come pick him up.

17:03.380 --> 17:04.619
Being busy is a good thing

17:04.619 --> 17:05.619
for young people.

17:06.390 --> 17:08.349
Well, I'll head home then.

17:08.369 --> 17:11.000
I'll come visit you and Auntie Fang
some other day.

17:11.000 --> 17:12.000
Okay.

17:12.160 --> 17:13.270
Come over anytime

17:13.270 --> 17:14.400
when you are free.

17:16.160 --> 17:17.220
I'm hanging up now.

17:17.240 --> 17:17.680
Okay.

17:17.960 --> 17:18.550
Bye.

19:04.320 --> 19:05.950
Qi, my dear Qi,

19:07.160 --> 19:08.160
I was wondering

19:08.160 --> 19:09.820
why you had to stay in Haizhou.

19:10.560 --> 19:12.760
It turns out you meant to get even for me.

19:14.960 --> 19:15.530
Love you.

19:43.880 --> 19:44.610
Hansheng...

19:48.030 --> 19:48.880
Hansheng...

19:50.640 --> 19:51.370
Hansheng...

19:55.490 --> 19:56.950
Professor Jiang is on the way here.

19:56.950 --> 19:58.010
He'll arrive soon.

20:00.480 --> 20:01.070
Dan.

20:01.600 --> 20:02.400
How are you?

20:06.880 --> 20:07.550
I'm fine.

20:10.460 --> 20:11.920
Consider yourself lucky.

20:12.050 --> 20:13.890
Good thing you reacted fast
and were driving fast.

20:13.890 --> 20:15.660
That truck only hit the rear of your car,

20:15.660 --> 20:16.790
so you weren't hurt.

20:19.920 --> 20:20.510
Hello.

20:20.680 --> 20:22.400
Where is Zhou Jin? She's in Bed 11.

20:22.400 --> 20:23.350
The second room in there.

20:23.350 --> 20:23.880
Thanks.

20:25.350 --> 20:26.880
Are you Zhou Jin's husband?

20:27.110 --> 20:27.870
Yes, I am.

20:28.790 --> 20:30.440
Here's a package for you.

20:32.870 --> 20:33.790
Who sent it?

20:34.070 --> 20:35.130
Some delivery guy.

20:48.650 --> 20:50.500
[Professor Jiang, let's play the game
another way]

20:50.500 --> 20:52.360
[I'll hurt whoever you try to protect.
Is it fun?]

21:11.790 --> 21:13.750
Where can I watch
the surveillance footage?

21:13.750 --> 21:15.880
I'm really fine. Don't worry about me.

21:15.890 --> 21:17.020
I'm perfectly well.

21:22.590 --> 21:23.550
I can get off work now,

21:23.550 --> 21:25.010
as he's here to replace me.

21:25.440 --> 21:26.870
Your husband's waiting downstairs, right?

21:26.870 --> 21:27.830
Yes, exactly.

21:28.550 --> 21:29.280
Don't worry.

21:29.440 --> 21:31.170
The doctor said she's all fine.

21:31.680 --> 21:32.540
I'll take off then.

21:32.540 --> 21:34.020
Hansheng, walk Dan out.

21:34.320 --> 21:35.880
No need. I'm good on my own.

21:38.600 --> 21:40.130
Sorry for the trouble, Dan.

21:57.230 --> 21:58.400
Why just stand there?

21:58.400 --> 21:59.030
Come here.

22:10.870 --> 22:11.750
Does it hurt?

22:13.680 --> 22:14.400
Yes.

22:15.440 --> 22:16.640
It hurts a lot.

22:17.210 --> 22:18.610
My shoulders are aching,

22:18.770 --> 22:20.370
and my head is buzzing.

22:21.090 --> 22:22.350
Where else is hurting?

22:23.480 --> 22:25.010
Every other part of my body.

22:25.680 --> 22:27.590
I feel like I can't move at all.

22:33.240 --> 22:34.030
Don't just stand there.

22:34.030 --> 22:34.720
Take a seat.

22:45.920 --> 22:46.720
What is it

22:47.070 --> 22:47.960
with you?

22:49.310 --> 22:50.640
You're acting strange.

22:57.490 --> 22:59.140
Did my master run his mouth

22:59.480 --> 23:00.810
and tell you something?

23:04.160 --> 23:04.880
Hansheng,

23:05.510 --> 23:07.310
I must confess something to you.

23:08.640 --> 23:09.310
Today,

23:11.590 --> 23:13.310
I dropped by my old apartment

23:14.350 --> 23:15.350
with Jiang Cheng.

23:16.350 --> 23:17.110
I brought him there

23:17.110 --> 23:19.050
only because he has nowhere to live now.

23:19.050 --> 23:20.400
The team approved of him

23:20.430 --> 23:21.950
staying there for a while.

23:22.400 --> 23:23.590
So I went there with him

23:23.590 --> 23:25.050
and tidied things up a bit.

23:27.400 --> 23:28.240
It was just one hour.

23:28.240 --> 23:29.550
I only spent one hour with him.

23:29.550 --> 23:30.110
Really.

23:30.200 --> 23:31.160
I left right after.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.220
Nothing happened.

23:32.400 --> 23:33.200
Rest assured.

23:41.960 --> 23:42.690
That's nice.

23:46.920 --> 23:49.380
Jiang Cheng is truly able
to take care of you.

23:50.820 --> 23:51.750
Jiang Hansheng,

23:53.750 --> 23:55.430
do you even hear yourself?

24:06.960 --> 24:07.720
Zhou Jin,

24:10.720 --> 24:11.480
I love you.

24:17.340 --> 24:17.970
Hansheng,

24:19.910 --> 24:21.710
I know I've been behaving poorly

24:22.610 --> 24:23.780
these days.

24:23.810 --> 24:24.870
We should split up.

24:28.880 --> 24:29.680
What?

24:34.790 --> 24:35.920
Let's get a divorce.

24:37.310 --> 24:38.510
I'm serious about it.

24:51.540 --> 24:52.170
Hansheng,

24:52.510 --> 24:53.030
I...

24:53.030 --> 24:54.160
I know I haven't played the part

24:54.160 --> 24:55.560
of a good wife these days.

24:55.750 --> 24:57.550
I've neglected your feelings.

24:57.550 --> 24:57.960
But...

24:57.960 --> 24:59.820
You're not in the wrong, Zhou Jin.

25:01.480 --> 25:02.740
This isn't your fault.

25:04.160 --> 25:05.420
The problem is with me.

25:06.720 --> 25:08.000
We're not right for each other.

25:08.000 --> 25:09.600
What's the problem with you?

25:10.030 --> 25:11.030
How are we not right for each other?

25:11.030 --> 25:12.960
Have you ever asked for my opinion?

25:13.500 --> 25:15.630
Everything's perfectly fine with us.

25:16.330 --> 25:17.260
What is going on?

25:21.510 --> 25:22.160
Zhou Jin.

25:24.900 --> 25:27.230
You've only grown used
to me being around.

25:27.850 --> 25:29.400
But habits can be broken easily.

25:29.400 --> 25:31.480
Jiang Hansheng, what's wrong with you?

25:31.480 --> 25:33.140
Why are you spewing nonsense?

25:44.270 --> 25:46.200
Zhou Jin, let me ask you a question.

25:47.680 --> 25:49.920
No need to take my feelings
into consideration.

25:49.920 --> 25:51.520
Just give me a candid answer.

25:55.350 --> 25:56.030
Ask away.

26:01.640 --> 26:02.480
If you had known

26:02.480 --> 26:04.680
Jiang Cheng's identity from the start,

26:05.720 --> 26:08.180
would I have stood any chance
with you at all?

26:19.570 --> 26:20.500
There are no ifs.

26:20.840 --> 26:21.470
Answer me.

26:21.710 --> 26:22.570
I don't want to.

26:37.640 --> 26:38.970
We both know the answer.

26:41.270 --> 26:42.200
Jiang Hansheng,

26:43.030 --> 26:43.640
you are

26:44.510 --> 26:46.240
being jealous in the wrong way.

26:49.790 --> 26:51.440
We are already married.

26:51.550 --> 26:53.680
It's good that Jiang Cheng is back now.

26:54.200 --> 26:54.880
This way,

26:55.720 --> 26:57.320
things will be easier for us.

26:59.160 --> 27:01.820
You won't be shackled
by this marriage anymore.

27:03.240 --> 27:04.770
Are you deciding for me now?

27:07.350 --> 27:08.680
I will pack up your stuff

27:09.350 --> 27:10.950
and put it in the police dorm.

27:11.350 --> 27:12.810
Before the case is solved,

27:13.070 --> 27:14.330
you should stay there.

27:15.030 --> 27:16.490
Let's be apart for a while.

27:17.550 --> 27:19.070
We're getting a divorce anyway.

27:19.070 --> 27:20.870
Why even bother where I'll stay?

27:24.400 --> 27:25.030
Whatever.

27:26.630 --> 27:28.560
Jiang Hansheng, stop right there!

27:31.400 --> 27:33.460
You're a real character, aren't you?

27:34.640 --> 27:35.290
Back then,

27:35.960 --> 27:38.690
I proposed marriage to you
in this very hospital.

27:38.720 --> 27:39.480
And now,

27:39.750 --> 27:42.250
you're asking for a divorce
in the same place, huh?

27:42.250 --> 27:43.360
Do you remember

27:43.860 --> 27:45.090
what you promised me?

27:47.250 --> 27:47.970
You said

27:49.270 --> 27:50.530
you would never hurt me

27:51.070 --> 27:52.440
or betray me.

27:54.480 --> 27:55.610
Have you forgotten?

27:58.550 --> 27:59.110
Zhou Jin,

28:00.640 --> 28:01.440
I promise you.

28:02.510 --> 28:03.510
I won't hurt you

28:04.400 --> 28:05.480
or betray you.

28:15.880 --> 28:16.590
Sorry.

28:17.880 --> 28:18.940
I broke my promise.

28:20.480 --> 28:21.240
Jiang Hansheng!

28:21.240 --> 28:25.080
♪ I never want you to bear the pain ♪

28:22.880 --> 28:24.000
Jiang Hansheng, don't you dare go!

28:24.000 --> 28:24.790
What happened?

28:24.790 --> 28:26.400
You can't leave the ward yet.

28:28.490 --> 28:33.090
♪ I'm about to exhaust all I have ♪

28:35.840 --> 28:39.590
♪ Trading time with touching moments ♪

28:40.350 --> 28:43.430
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

28:45.350 --> 28:47.580
♪ They're so free ♪

28:49.820 --> 28:52.900
♪ How can I tell you ♪

28:52.920 --> 28:56.550
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

28:57.220 --> 29:00.040
♪ I am sure to ♪

29:00.080 --> 29:03.620
♪ Walk with you ♪

29:02.160 --> 29:03.270
My phone...

29:04.650 --> 29:08.120
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

29:08.000 --> 29:08.960
Where's my phone?

29:08.150 --> 29:12.270
♪ One more glance is not enough ♪

29:12.290 --> 29:14.510
♪ At the crossroad ♪

29:13.720 --> 29:16.270
Where is my phone?

29:14.540 --> 29:17.910
♪ To the left or right ♪

29:18.910 --> 29:22.830
♪ I want to hold your hand ♪

29:43.350 --> 29:44.550
Why did you come here?

29:46.240 --> 29:47.900
Do you not like living with me?

29:48.220 --> 29:51.300
♪ How can I tell you ♪

29:49.880 --> 29:51.320
Do you still have feelings for him?

29:51.320 --> 29:54.950
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

29:53.160 --> 29:54.220
How is Jiang Cheng?

29:55.110 --> 29:56.510
I know you've been worried about him.

29:55.620 --> 29:58.440
♪ I am sure to ♪

29:57.920 --> 29:58.720
Don't worry.

29:58.480 --> 30:02.020
♪ Walk with you ♪

29:59.960 --> 30:00.890
I'll be with you.

30:01.880 --> 30:02.880
Over these years,

30:03.050 --> 30:06.520
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

30:04.160 --> 30:05.760
you've really changed a lot.

30:06.550 --> 30:10.110
♪ Every minute and second with you
is not a luxury ♪

30:10.480 --> 30:11.400
Please sit down.

30:10.610 --> 30:12.200
♪ At the crossroad ♪

30:12.230 --> 30:15.930
♪ To the left or right ♪

30:13.640 --> 30:14.480
If you had known

30:14.480 --> 30:16.680
Jiang Cheng's identity from the start,

30:17.500 --> 30:20.640
♪ We'll eventually hold hands ♪

30:17.640 --> 30:20.100
would I have stood any chance
with you at all?

30:51.550 --> 30:52.640
Grandpa,

30:52.640 --> 30:54.480
why haven't you come see me?

30:54.480 --> 30:57.400
When will you finish catching bad guys?

30:58.590 --> 30:59.680
Sweetheart,

30:59.920 --> 31:01.440
when I'm done catching bad guys,

31:01.440 --> 31:02.510
I'll go be with you.

31:04.310 --> 31:06.510
Okay, Grandpa. Go to bed early.

31:07.880 --> 31:08.680
I'll obey.

31:08.700 --> 31:09.780
I will.

31:13.240 --> 31:13.750
Dad,

31:14.030 --> 31:15.350
it's me, Li.

31:16.550 --> 31:18.110
I need to tell you something.

31:18.110 --> 31:20.130
Chief Zhan from the Information Department
just had a baby.

31:20.130 --> 31:20.970
He's holding

31:21.000 --> 31:22.830
a one-month celebration
at Longxing Hotel in a few days.

31:22.830 --> 31:25.030
He has always wanted to invite you to it.

31:25.400 --> 31:26.920
Why don't you

31:26.920 --> 31:28.000
take some time out for it?

31:28.000 --> 31:29.310
His baby is so adorable.

31:29.310 --> 31:29.920
Well,

31:30.510 --> 31:32.920
I'm not familiar with those
in the Information Department.

31:32.920 --> 31:34.680
I'd rather not attend the event.

31:34.680 --> 31:35.720
Listen, Dad.

31:36.440 --> 31:38.240
Chief Zhan is above me after all.

31:38.590 --> 31:40.720
I have a visitor now. Talk to you later.

31:41.590 --> 31:42.110
Come in!

31:59.400 --> 32:00.730
What are you doing here?

32:02.270 --> 32:02.830
Prof,

32:04.480 --> 32:06.410
I think I've messed everything up.

32:11.840 --> 32:14.030
Zhou Jin's car accident wasn't by chance.

32:14.030 --> 32:14.830
I've checked.

32:15.400 --> 32:17.200
The delivery guy who sent this over

32:17.200 --> 32:19.090
hid where cameras couldn't catch him.

32:19.090 --> 32:20.020
I can't find him.

32:25.000 --> 32:26.260
Are you divorcing Zhou

32:27.110 --> 32:28.640
just because of this?

32:32.160 --> 32:32.920
Pup,

32:32.950 --> 32:33.870
why stare at me?

32:34.110 --> 32:34.970
Say something.

32:40.030 --> 32:41.790
It's not safe for her to be with me.

32:41.790 --> 32:43.920
It's even less safe for her to be alone.

32:48.000 --> 32:49.060
She won't be alone.

32:50.310 --> 32:51.160
I told her

32:51.590 --> 32:54.000
to stay in the police dorm
at Nancheng Branch

32:54.000 --> 32:55.130
and never come back.

32:59.750 --> 33:02.270
So you ran away from home

33:02.270 --> 33:04.550
and came to my place in the rain.

33:05.510 --> 33:06.270
Right?

33:11.110 --> 33:11.840
Impressive.

33:12.870 --> 33:14.870
You're unbelievable.

33:20.550 --> 33:21.110
Prof,

33:21.720 --> 33:22.640
hear me out.

33:23.710 --> 33:25.510
I want a divorce for two reasons.

33:26.160 --> 33:26.680
First,

33:27.660 --> 33:28.720
Qi Yan will only act

33:28.750 --> 33:30.550
crazier and crazier from now on.

33:31.210 --> 33:33.410
When the police destroyed
the drug factory,

33:33.410 --> 33:35.370
they not only rescued
Yao Weihai's undercover agent,

33:35.370 --> 33:36.040
but also removed

33:36.040 --> 33:38.370
the mole Qi Yan planted inside the police.

33:39.370 --> 33:40.950
One single happening of these

33:40.950 --> 33:42.550
was enough to infuriate him,

33:43.480 --> 33:44.880
let alone piling them up.

33:46.110 --> 33:48.510
Zhou Jin's car crash
looks like an accident

33:49.300 --> 33:51.300
probably just because
she reacted fast enough

33:51.300 --> 33:52.900
to avoid being harmed by him.

33:53.550 --> 33:54.510
Qi Yan once said

33:56.000 --> 33:57.930
he would make my life a living hell.

34:01.070 --> 34:03.070
I know what you're saying.

34:05.130 --> 34:06.590
What's the second reason?

34:13.030 --> 34:14.030
It's Jiang Cheng.

34:18.860 --> 34:20.840
He turned back to being Officer Jiang
from Cangfeng.

34:20.840 --> 34:23.570
People have basically recognized
his identity.

34:23.920 --> 34:24.920
He will often show up

34:24.920 --> 34:26.670
in Zhou Jin's life from now on.

34:31.280 --> 34:32.550
So,

34:32.550 --> 34:34.610
you wanted to play the noble guy, huh?

34:36.719 --> 34:39.250
Then you just stood up with chivalry
and said,

34:39.920 --> 34:40.969
"Comrade Zhou,

34:41.880 --> 34:42.710
off you go.

34:43.710 --> 34:44.800
I'm backing out."

34:50.030 --> 34:51.110
I won't back out.

34:51.670 --> 34:53.510
I will still protect her in secret

34:53.510 --> 34:54.480
like I used to.

34:55.840 --> 34:58.000
Then you should've said to her like this:

34:58.000 --> 34:58.800
"Zhou Jin,

35:01.030 --> 35:02.000
off you go.

35:03.710 --> 35:04.760
I'm backing out."

35:11.590 --> 35:13.190
Prof, stop making fun of me.

35:13.320 --> 35:13.840
Jiang Hansheng,

35:13.840 --> 35:15.480
you broke up with Zhou

35:15.480 --> 35:17.710
before I could attend your wedding.

35:18.230 --> 35:19.830
Have you thought about this?

35:19.920 --> 35:20.550
The situation...

35:20.550 --> 35:23.760
Everything is different now from before.

35:25.440 --> 35:26.890
You heartlessly

35:27.590 --> 35:29.030
abandoned and deserted Zhou

35:29.030 --> 35:30.320
just like that.

35:31.110 --> 35:33.110
And you think you were being

35:33.800 --> 35:34.840
nice to her, huh?

35:40.920 --> 35:43.050
I only meant to free her from shackles.

35:48.340 --> 35:49.260
Hansheng,

35:50.450 --> 35:52.450
if you really divorce Zhou,

35:54.110 --> 35:55.550
will you stop loving her?

35:57.110 --> 35:59.990
Qi Yan is a sociopath.

36:01.070 --> 36:02.360
Do you think he cares

36:02.360 --> 36:04.020
if the two of you are divorced?

36:05.220 --> 36:06.220
Besides,

36:07.630 --> 36:10.290
do you wish to let Jiang Cheng
have what he wants,

36:11.000 --> 36:13.400
or are you actually
afraid of losing to him?

36:19.230 --> 36:21.830
Your care for someone may cloud
your judgment.

37:09.030 --> 37:09.760
You're back.

37:12.990 --> 37:13.860
What happened?

37:17.420 --> 37:19.080
I got in a fight with Hansheng.

37:19.100 --> 37:20.560
You got in a fight with him?

37:20.970 --> 37:22.370
The National Little Rose

37:22.410 --> 37:23.410
is quite prickly.

37:24.080 --> 37:25.190
He is, indeed.

37:25.670 --> 37:27.470
He packed my luggage quite well.

37:34.160 --> 37:35.620
The two of you got in a fight

37:35.890 --> 37:37.620
because of Jiang Cheng, right?

37:37.770 --> 37:38.540
I don't know.

37:39.850 --> 37:40.700
At first,

37:41.310 --> 37:43.370
I thought the reason was Jiang Cheng.

37:44.290 --> 37:45.510
I explained and apologized

37:45.510 --> 37:46.380
to Hansheng.

37:47.800 --> 37:48.570
Later on...

37:49.620 --> 37:51.220
I don't know what led to this.

37:51.730 --> 37:53.550
Actually, I completely understand you.

37:53.550 --> 37:55.330
People only have limited energy.

37:55.330 --> 37:57.310
You've been fully occupied by work lately

37:57.310 --> 37:58.680
and thus neglected Professor Jiang.

37:58.680 --> 38:00.020
Speaking from my own experience,

38:00.020 --> 38:01.590
I think he is probably asking

38:01.590 --> 38:02.590
for attention

38:02.960 --> 38:04.220
by triggering a fight.

38:04.330 --> 38:05.980
I thought the same.

38:06.310 --> 38:07.880
So told him he was being jealous

38:07.880 --> 38:09.400
in the wrong way.

38:09.580 --> 38:11.180
He and I are already married,

38:11.620 --> 38:13.220
but he still wants a divorce.

38:13.280 --> 38:14.090
Divorce?

38:15.420 --> 38:16.690
Impossible.

38:16.720 --> 38:18.250
He must be making nonsense.

38:18.910 --> 38:19.790
I know him well.

38:20.970 --> 38:22.230
He is serious about it.

38:22.710 --> 38:24.310
He truly wants to divorce me.

38:27.330 --> 38:28.160
In fact,

38:28.770 --> 38:30.720
as police officers,
especially female ones,

38:30.720 --> 38:32.070
it's really hard to strike

38:32.070 --> 38:34.000
a balance between family and work.

38:34.190 --> 38:35.520
I've been through this.

38:35.870 --> 38:36.910
My husband and I

38:37.170 --> 38:38.300
went to college together.

38:38.300 --> 38:39.830
We were chummy all the time.

38:39.850 --> 38:42.110
We didn't argue even after having a baby.

38:42.330 --> 38:42.940
However,

38:44.550 --> 38:45.410
a few years ago,

38:45.610 --> 38:47.180
because of my work,

38:47.960 --> 38:49.290
we nearly got a divorce.

38:50.370 --> 38:52.370
Coincidentally, during that time,

38:53.030 --> 38:54.490
what cases was I handling?

38:55.900 --> 38:56.830
Rape and murder.

38:57.190 --> 38:59.320
Cheating husbands killed their wives.

38:59.320 --> 39:02.250
As a result,
I found all males physically repulsive.

39:02.780 --> 39:04.720
When I was home,
everything my husband did annoyed me.

39:04.720 --> 39:07.180
He looked like a huge scumbag to
me in any way.

39:08.810 --> 39:10.010
Hilarious, isn't it?

39:12.690 --> 39:14.810
This actually reflects a problem.

39:15.240 --> 39:15.760
That is,

39:16.360 --> 39:19.710
bringing home negative emotions from work

39:19.860 --> 39:21.320
is an utterly awful thing.

39:22.750 --> 39:24.610
In retrospect, my husband told me

39:24.760 --> 39:27.280
that I was harsh on him about everything,

39:27.300 --> 39:28.900
and that I had a short temper.

39:29.750 --> 39:30.520
You see,

39:30.780 --> 39:32.240
between husband and wife,

39:32.280 --> 39:33.890
once there is a rift,

39:33.920 --> 39:36.180
they would even argue over trivialities

39:36.350 --> 39:38.440
and refuse to give in to each other.

39:38.980 --> 39:40.790
In the end, we got tired of arguing.

39:40.790 --> 39:41.920
I thought to myself,

39:41.940 --> 39:42.740
"Why the fuss?

39:42.810 --> 39:43.980
Maybe a divorce is needed,

39:43.980 --> 39:46.980
since we're torturing each other
by being together."

39:48.240 --> 39:49.970
But then you two made up, right?

39:50.320 --> 39:51.480
Of course we did.

39:51.570 --> 39:53.980
I couldn't have easily let him go,

39:54.010 --> 39:54.850
right?

39:55.240 --> 39:57.240
Do you know how we patched things up?

39:58.440 --> 39:59.190
One day,

39:59.810 --> 40:00.940
he got drunk

40:00.960 --> 40:02.160
and came to my office.

40:02.230 --> 40:03.960
That eight-foot-tall guy

40:04.290 --> 40:06.420
held onto my legs and cried.

40:06.450 --> 40:07.930
People were watching,

40:08.840 --> 40:09.840
yet he didn't feel embarrassed

40:09.840 --> 40:11.240
or fear being laughed at.

40:11.700 --> 40:12.700
He said to me,

40:13.900 --> 40:15.100
"For all these years,

40:15.330 --> 40:16.840
I've been supportive of your job,

40:16.840 --> 40:18.280
done all the housework,

40:18.460 --> 40:19.990
and taken care of our child.

40:20.560 --> 40:21.630
I'm a man, but is it wrong

40:21.630 --> 40:23.050
for me to ask for some love and care?

40:23.050 --> 40:25.200
Why do you have to divorce me?"

40:26.500 --> 40:27.360
At that moment,

40:28.540 --> 40:29.670
I suddenly realized

40:29.920 --> 40:30.710
that

40:32.090 --> 40:33.530
my behavior misled him.

40:34.750 --> 40:35.600
Also,

40:36.070 --> 40:37.280
over all those years,

40:38.120 --> 40:39.750
he had really suffered a lot.

40:41.920 --> 40:43.250
So, I decided right away

40:43.360 --> 40:45.280
to absolutely not divorce him.

40:50.680 --> 40:52.810
Dan, I understand what you're saying.

40:53.420 --> 40:55.220
I've done some thinking as well.

40:55.270 --> 40:56.730
I haven't done well enough

40:56.900 --> 40:58.030
as a wife these days.

40:58.800 --> 40:59.650
It's my fault.

41:02.420 --> 41:04.350
But things between me and Hansheng

41:05.710 --> 41:07.110
are different from those

41:07.920 --> 41:09.580
between you and your husband.

41:10.360 --> 41:11.620
We're in a somewhat...

41:12.960 --> 41:14.090
complex situation.

41:14.840 --> 41:16.360
The reason of it being complex

41:16.360 --> 41:17.490
lies in you, not him.

41:24.510 --> 41:25.960
He asked me a question,

41:26.710 --> 41:28.110
but I answered it poorly.

41:30.070 --> 41:30.960
What question?

41:31.280 --> 41:32.150
He asked

41:33.280 --> 41:34.550
how would I have chosen

41:34.710 --> 41:35.910
if I had known earlier

41:36.960 --> 41:39.160
that Jiang Cheng was an undercover cop.

41:42.000 --> 41:43.200
What was your answer?

41:45.760 --> 41:46.890
I couldn't give one.

41:48.000 --> 41:50.840
Neither did I have the courage
to tell him the truth.

41:50.840 --> 41:53.170
It definitely would've broken his heart.

41:53.960 --> 41:55.320
Because the truth is,

41:55.630 --> 41:56.710
if I had known earlier

41:56.710 --> 41:59.040
that Jiang Cheng was an undercover cop...

42:02.000 --> 42:03.930
I wouldn't have married Hansheng.

42:17.640 --> 42:19.000
You were both wrong.

42:19.760 --> 42:21.550
Professor Jiang shouldn't have asked
such a question,

42:21.550 --> 42:23.610
and you didn't have to answer it at all.

42:23.610 --> 42:25.450
Time never goes backwards.

42:25.650 --> 42:27.580
There aren't that many ifs in life.

42:30.440 --> 42:31.100
The fact...

42:32.300 --> 42:33.340
What is the fact?

42:34.270 --> 42:34.980
The fact is,

42:35.010 --> 42:37.390
you went through
five agonizing years alone

42:37.390 --> 42:39.250
until Professor Jiang showed up.

42:39.830 --> 42:41.160
He cherishes you.

42:41.690 --> 42:43.050
He gives you confidence.

42:43.050 --> 42:45.530
He makes you happy again.

42:48.940 --> 42:50.270
From your perspective,

42:50.670 --> 42:53.000
why did you refuse to answer his question?

42:54.180 --> 42:56.180
Because you care about his feelings

42:56.240 --> 42:57.760
and that you hate to hurt him.

42:57.760 --> 42:58.890
What does that mean?

43:00.490 --> 43:01.180
That means

43:03.570 --> 43:04.680
you're in love with him.
